ckquote>我住Lisbon，有咩問題可以問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲酒食tapas睇海 有咩推介？"},{"pid":"4551a02224645ff44b51d07c01f54d9d989d154d","tid":201560,"uid":97997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T21:37:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我住Lisbon，有咩問題可以問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲酒食tapas睇海 有咩推介？</blockquote><br />\nTapas 去西班牙食，呢度係食海鮮，我食過呢兩間<br />\n第二條link果間隔離有間食沙甸魚，好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nRestaurante Furnas do Guincho<br />\nSintra-Cascais Natural Park, Guincho, 2750-642 Cascais, Portugal<br />\n+351 21 486 9243<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/PF17PFELnmS2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FPF17PFELnmS2&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=37de4f91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/PF17PFELnmS2</a><br />\n<br />\nRestaurante Os Prazeres Da Carne<br />\nSintra-Cascais Natural Park, Avenida Nossa Senhora Cabo Quinta 101, 2750-374 Cascais, Portugal<br />\n+351 21 484 3334<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/L8woKdUj5B52\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FL8woKdUj5B52&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=d233f0e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/L8woKdUj5B52</a>"},{"pid":"809fbcb3a907591489fea81bef86a6bdf9cdd842","tid":201560,"uid":42090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我中意波圖多啲，老老實實火車都係兩個幾鐘 一程百二，咁都嫌貴？</blockquote><br />\n係上網book? 我睇緊porto去lisbon既交通，見到最平巴士都要二百港紙左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有無搵過機票呀?<br />\n我搵返我之前坐過果班機<br />\n單程$84...依加五月尾既仲有位<br />\n<br />\n我以為你講係時間問題...點知係錢既問題<br />\n幾百蚊都唔係咩錢啦..唔去你自己後悔<br />\n兩個地方都好正"},{"pid":"fa48ac23cfd871d65d4221eee62243bc3af68b66","tid":201560,"uid